The three-day initiation course for future glaciers was very successful and attracted visitors from all over the world.
Special chocolate ice cream classes are also offered over several days, and hands-on sessions are held in the private ice cream parlor.
In the midst of the mid-40s crisis, a number of people are dreaming of a new career, others are simply risking their burning desire on the smooth ice.
This time, 40 participants from 19 countries from all continents, from Brazil to Saudi Arabia to Hungary.
Jacky, an art education teacher from California, is a fan of the Slow Food movement and wants to offer a quality European product in the future in the country of Industrial Ice.
